org.vast.data

Class BaseTreeVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vast.data.BaseTreeVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataComponentVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataStructFilter, ScalarVisitor

    public abstract class BaseTreeVisitor
extends Object
implements DataComponentVisitor

    Abstract tree visitor providing logic to visit nested data components recursively. By default, the visit methods for scalar and range components do nothing.

    Since:
    Oct 9, 2015
    Author:
    Alex Robin
